--------------------------- WEAPONS --------------------------------
ARES PREDATOR III
- Base Damage: 9P + net hits
- AP: -1 | APDS: -5 [SITUATIONAL: APDS ammo]
- Dice Pool: 16 [ALWAYS ACTIVE: Smartlink] [SITUATIONAL: Heavy Pistols spec]
- Average vs. typical target: 13P-15P (assuming 4-6 net hits)
- Mode: SA | Ammo: 15(c)

--------------------------- ARMOR ----------------------------------
ARMOR JACKET
- Base: 12 | +Ballistic Mask 2 = 14 [STACKS: Mask adds to jacket]
- Soak: Body 5 + Armor 14 = 19 dice
- Average soak: 6-7 hits
- Note: AP reduces armor before soak

CHAMELEON SUIT
- Base: 9 | +Ballistic Mask 2 = 11 [STACKS: Mask adds to suit]
- Soak: Body 5 + Armor 11 = 16 dice
- +2 Sneaking [SITUATIONAL: Chameleon Suit, WHEN CAMO ACTIVE in wilderness/urban]
- Average soak: 5-6 hits

--------------------------- COMBAT MECHANICS FLOW ------------------
[FOR LLM USE - Apply in this order when resolving attacks]

1. ATTACK ROLL: Player rolls weapon skill pool vs. target's Dodge
2. NET HITS: If player wins, add net hits to weapon base damage
   Formula: Final DV = Weapon Base Damage + (net hits)
3. ARMOR PENETRATION: Target's armor is reduced by weapon AP
   Formula: Effective Armor = Target Armor - Weapon AP
   - AP value varies by weapon and ammo type
4. SOAK ROLL: Target rolls Body + Effective Armor
5. FINAL DAMAGE: Final DV - soak hits = damage taken
   - Apply to Physical or Stun track based on damage type (P/S)

EXAMPLE (Trick with Ares Predator III, APDS):
Player shoots security guard (Body 3, Armor 12) with APDS, gets 3 net hits.
- Weapon: Ares Predator III (9P, AP -1 + APDS -4 = -5 total)
- Final DV: 9P + 3 = 12P
- Effective Armor: 12 - 5 = 7
- Soak roll: Body 3 + 7 = 10 dice (avg 3 hits)
- Final damage: 12P - 3 = 9P damage

