- Recoil: -1 per shot after first [SITUATIONAL]
- Low-light conditions: +2 [SITUATIONAL]
- Target behind partial cover: -2 [SITUATIONAL]

SOCIAL:
- Negotiating from weakness: -2 [SITUATIONAL]
- Intimidation with leverage/physical threat: +2 [SITUATIONAL]
- Con vs. suspicious target: -2 to -4 [SITUATIONAL]
- First Impression: Already included (+2) [FIRST ENCOUNTER ONLY]
- Impersonating known person: +2 [SITUATIONAL: Social Chameleon]

STEALTH (Sneaking):
- Observers alert: -2 [SITUATIONAL]
- Moving at half speed: +2 [SITUATIONAL]
- Chameleon Suit active: +2 [SITUATIONAL: CAMO ACTIVE]

PERCEPTION:
